Wheatland R-II School District is a school district in Hickory County, Missouri with a jurisdiction over Wheatland, Missouri and the surrounding area. WSD has a graduation rate of 100%, 71% are eligible for free or reduced price lunches, 56% of students head to college after graduation. The average teacher salary is $36,119. The school district spends $10,653 per student, slightly less than the national average 


== Schools ==


==== Elementary ====
Wheatland Elementary (PreK-6)


==== High School ====
Wheatland High School (6-12)


